328
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,360
Love is mutual.

329
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:09,750
So is medical technology.

330
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:12,870
Technology for our country

331
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:14,910
