00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:19,110
Delivery.

452
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:54,670
Xing.

453
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:05,590
Xing?

454
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:12,940
(Xing)

455
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,080
Where are you?

456
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:16,960
Mr. Han.

457
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,880
Long time no see.

458
00:26:22,350 --> 00:26:23,200
Zhu Houyu.

459
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,000
Surprised, huh?

460
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:27,750
I climbed out of the hell.

461
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:29,920
Where is Ji Xing?

462
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:31,750
You miss her?

463
00:26:36,790 --> 00:26:37,630
Fine.

464
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:40,000
I'll let you hear her scream.

465
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:11,590
How does it sound?

466
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:12,960
Beautiful, huh?

467
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,510
You have a death wish!

468
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:19,680
Threaten me?

469
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:22,670
Han Ting,

470
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,000
I'm a desperado now.

471
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:28,790
Five million dollars.

472
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:30,680
And you come alone.

473
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:34,200
On the rooftop of the workshop

474
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,040
of Xinggang Steel.

475
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:36,960
If you dare to call the police,

476
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:39,920
I promise you

477
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:41,640
she can never speak again.

478
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,550
Don't blame me.

479
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:49,960
Blame Han Ting instead.

480
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:52,750
I had planned to kidnap him.

481
00:27:54,110 --> 00:27:55,750
But you were there in his flat.

482
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:58,550
Now, I look

483
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:00,070
really terrible

484
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,240
and it's all because of him.

485
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,160
Ten years.

486
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:10,400
My company developed for ten years.

487
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,790
My hard work

488
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:18,750
was completely ruined by him.

489
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:23,200
More than a thousand employees

490
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:26,750
lost their jobs overnight.

491
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,160
Did I mess with him?

492
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,960
Why did he do this to me?

493
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:39,960
Now, there's no turning back for me.

494
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,790
When he wants me to die,

495
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,550
he has to die with me.

496
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,440
To be honest,

497
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,070
I don't want the money.

498
00:28:58,350 --> 00:28:59,640
I don't want reconciliation, either.

499
00:29:00,440 --> 00:29:02,270
I'm going to kill him!

500
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:10,460
(Tang Song)

501
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,750
Boss, what's up?

502
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:13,400
Ji Xing was kidnapped by Zhu Houyu.

503
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:14,680
In the old workshop of Xinggang Steel.

504
00:29:14,750 --> 00:29:15,590
Call the police.

505
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:16,480
Where are you now?

506
00:29:16,830 --> 00:29:17,670
Don't be impulsive.

507
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:18,680
Wait until we arrive.

508
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,440
Boss, do you hear?

509
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:22,350
Hello?

510
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:01,920
Come up here!

511
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:25,510
It's brave of you, Mr. Han.

512
00:30:30,750 --> 00:30:31,590
Stop!

513
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:36,760
Mr. Han,

514
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:38,510
where's the money?

515
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,920
Do you not want to give it to me?

516
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:44,680
I'll give you the money.

517
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:47,000
Release her first.

518
00:30:47,510 --> 00:30:48,680
Don't even try that.

519
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,560
Give me the money!

520
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,000
Otherwise...

521
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,960
- I'll push her off!
- Wait.

522
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:00,110
The money is in the car.

523
00:31:01,510 --> 00:31:02,350
After you take the money,

524
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,550
you also need a car, don't you?

525
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,000
Fool me?

526
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:18,240
That's not five million!

527
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:19,310
You actually fooled me!

528
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:21,680
How can I get five million overnight?

529
00:31:23,310 --> 00:31:24,350
What's in the bag

530
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,070
is worth two million.

531
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,960
The rest is in this card.

532
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:34,430
Let her go.

533
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:38,480
I didn't expect the extremely arrogant Mr. Han

534
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,400
to be a hopeless romantic.

535
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:42,760
Fine.

536
00:31:43,270 --> 00:31:44,510
You set me up first.

537
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:45,880
Taking the money from you

538
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:46,830
is too good for you.

539
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,240
I promise.

540
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:51,110
When I take your money,

541
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,640
I won't ask for more trouble.

542
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:54,590
You also have to promise

543
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:56,030
you will let me go.

544
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,510
I want money and you want her.

545
00:31:59,000 --> 00:31:59,880
Deal.

546
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:02,190
OK.

547
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,590
Leave.

548
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:54,160
From your full body check,

549
00:33:55,030 --> 00:33:56,270
your organs are all right.

550
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:02,350
How's the injury on your hand?

551
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:06,200
It's OK. Just some scratches. It's wrapped.

552
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:08,590
How is he?

553
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,920
Don't worry. Nothing is serious.

554
00:34:13,670 --> 00:34:15,000
The blood on his coat

555
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:17,150
was from his scratches.

556
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:18,870
But anyway,

557
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,840
he has a compression fracture
of the lumbar spine.

558
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:22,600
Recently,

559
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:24,590
you will feel intermittent pain.

560
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:27,510
Most importantly, you have to rest in bed.

561
00:34:28,110 --> 00:34:30,360
Especially the bruises and scratches on him...

562
00:34:31,110 --> 00:34:32,150
Take care of them carefully.

563
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:34,320
I'll get back to work.

564
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,920
Call me if you need anything.

565
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:36,800
OK.

566
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:37,760
Thank you.

567
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:56,920
The doctor asked you to rest well.

568
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:59,320
I'll lower the bed for you.

569
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,120
Xing.

570
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,150
Will you forgive me?

571
00:35:19,250 --> 00:35:23,960
♪Once again, you stand opposite me♪

572
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:29,950
♪Telling the worlds I'm not familiar with♪

573
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:31,320
I forgave you a long time ago.

574
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:34,850
♪They seem remote♪

575
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:39,320
I asked you to "die for me"

576
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:40,670
just in a fit of anger.

577
00:35:41,070 --> 00:35:41,910
I know.

578
00:35:44,110 --> 00:35:45,320
It was just an accident.

579
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:47,320
Don't overthink.

580
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,120
Accident?

581
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:51,840
When you held Zhu Houyu

582
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:53,670
and fell, did you know

583
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:55,630
I might also jump off?

584
00:35:59,530 --> 00:36:02,190
♪Time puts walls up♪

585
00:36:02,850 --> 00:36:05,970
♪To keep my loneliness safe♪

586
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:07,920
Sometimes, you make me

587
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,150
feel insecure.

588
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,440
Han Ting, you're awesome.

589
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:15,030
You have tricks.

590
00:36:15,670 --> 00:36:16,710
You think big.

591
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:21,070
But you never tell me about your plans.

592
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,710
I've heard about the other side of you

593
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:26,030
from someone else.

594
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,760
In many cases, I feel...

595
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:32,030
You're very strange.

596
00:36:34,210 --> 00:36:37,100
♪Before we're relieved♪

597
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,920
You totally see through me.

598
00:36:41,630 --> 00:36:42,840
But I can't see through you.

599
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:46,150
I can't even see you clearly.

600
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:49,710
♪And roundabout probings♪

601
00:36:50,630 --> 00:36:53,320
I used to think
you were on the top of the mountain

602
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,480
while I was only halfway.

603
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:58,840
So, I couldn't feel the way you did.

604
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:02,030
Then I wanted to go up and see.

605
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,880
But now, I think...

606
00:37:06,190 --> 00:37:07,960
I want more than that.

607
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,920
I want to come up to you

608
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,670
and stay behind you.

609
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:21,980
♪The chess board is set,
leaving us with a dilemma♪

610
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,360
If we're together,

611
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,840
I'm afraid I'll love you more and more.

612
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:30,960
So, before that,

613
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:32,710
I want to know more about you.

614
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:36,110
I want to know what you think

615
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:37,760
and what you plan to do.

616
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,400
Even if one day,

617
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:43,030
you're involved in the gray areas,

618
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:44,510
I will still be

619
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,110
one of your guys.

620
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:47,840
Accomplice, exactly.

621
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:52,200
♪Instead of expectations♪

622
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:55,760
I want to know why I do this for you.

623
00:37:56,590 --> 00:37:58,150
Whatever happens in the future,

624
00:37:58,150 --> 00:37:59,840
I will be on your side.

625
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:02,630
I want to know who I stand up for.

626
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:09,160
♪It is truly terrible♪

627
00:38:16,670 --> 00:38:17,630
So, shall we

628
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:18,840
get back together?

629
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:22,840
Not the investor and entrepreneur,

630
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:26,030
not the superior and subordinate,

631
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:29,320
but Han Ting

632
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:33,800
and Ji Xing.

633
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:36,200
♪We've met by accident♪

634
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:43,700
♪The face in my memory gives me mood swings♪

635
00:38:44,730 --> 00:38:47,980
♪It tells something and it listens too♪

636
00:38:49,210 --> 00:38:52,680
♪This is the man I'm waiting for♪

637
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,980
♪I'm often exhausted♪

638
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:59,350
♪You're always there behind me♪

639
00:39:01,110 --> 00:39:02,000
Miss Ji,

640
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:04,630
this is our first meeting.

641
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,280
Nice to meet you.

642
00:39:08,410 --> 00:39:11,080
♪For you, I'm depressed♪

643
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:16,240
♪You realized that first♪

644
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:18,840
Nice to meet you, Mr. Han.

645
00:39:19,960 --> 00:39:25,070
♪We don't need to accept each other too fast♪

646
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:30,740
♪Nor do we need to love too rashly♪

647
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:37,580
♪We stay where we are, not going away♪

648
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:42,120
♪I expect one day♪

649
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:45,970
♪You will be back♪

650
00:39:46,610 --> 00:39:50,670
♪Talking first doesn't mean I give in♪

651
00:39:51,730 --> 00:39:56,360
♪No remarkable bet, either♪

652
00:39:57,500 --> 00:40:03,520
♪Starting over again, however sad I am♪

653
00:40:03,740 --> 00:40:08,160
♪I'll still love without hesitation♪

654
00:40:08,690 --> 00:40:13,510
♪Instead of passing on♪

655
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:21,150
Mr. Luo, you wanted to see me?

656
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:22,120
Take your seat.

657
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:27,150
Have you had

658
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,550
any trouble at work?

659
00:40:29,110 --> 00:40:31,030
Everybody is getting along very well.

660
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,840
We communicate smoothly, too.

661
00:40:34,110 --> 00:40:36,230
Mr. Luo, shall I report to you

662
00:40:36,230 --> 00:40:37,280
the project progress?

663
00:40:37,630 --> 00:40:38,470
No need.

664
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:39,960
I'm just caring

665
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:41,030
about your daily work.

666
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:43,110
I don't mean to push you.

667
00:40:44,160 --> 00:40:45,030
Rest assured.

668
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,510
Everything is going smoothly.

669
00:40:47,670 --> 00:40:48,510
That's good.

670
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,440
Last time, you did

671
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:52,000
technological innovation

672
00:40:52,190 --> 00:40:53,920
in 3D printing software

673
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:56,630
and made a great contribution.

674
00:40:57,190 --> 00:40:58,400
We all think highly of you.

675
00:40:59,150 --> 00:41:00,960
I'll live up to your expectations.

676
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:06,150
We have a great opportunity now.

677
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:09,360
We're going to send a technology executive

678
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:11,000
to Dongyang Base in Germany

679
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:13,760
as the deputy director
of the Technical Department.

680
00:41:14,070 --> 00:41:15,550
To work and further study

681
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:16,760
for three years.

682
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,320
When he's back in three years,

683
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,400
he'll be promoted

684
00:41:21,630 --> 00:41:23,670
to the Chief Technology Officer
of Hanhai Xingchen.

685
00:41:24,360 --> 00:41:25,400
Guys in Division 1

686
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:27,000
are keeping an eye on this opportunity.

687
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:29,280
But I think more highly of you.

688
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:32,070
I wonder if you're willing to go.

689
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:36,910
Mr. Luo,

690
00:41:38,030 --> 00:41:39,630
it's not a small thing.

691
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:41,670
And you told me so unexpectedly.

692
00:41:42,110 --> 00:41:42,950
I...

693
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,190
You don't need to reply now.

694
00:41:45,440 --> 00:41:47,230
The assignment will be in three months.

695
00:41:47,480 --> 00:41:49,000
Go back and think about it.

696
00:41:49,510 --> 00:41:50,630
I'd like to remind you, though.

697
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:52,070
It is a rare opportunity.

698
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:53,880
I hope you can seize it.

699
00:41:54,880 --> 00:41:55,960
I'm grateful to the cultivation

700
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:56,880
from you and our company.

701
00:41:57,070 --> 00:41:58,360
I'll think carefully about it.

702
00:42:27,190 --> 00:42:28,400
- Xing.
- Where do you hurt?

703
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:30,840
I'm fine. Just some scratches.

704
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:31,840
My wrist is bandaged.

705
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:33,070
Is it serious?

706
00:42:33,230 --> 00:42:34,070
No.

707
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:36,510
Did you get hurt anywhere else?

708
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:38,190
Don't keep it from us.

709
00:42:38,190 --> 00:42:39,030
Nowhere else.

710
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:41,230
What about Han Ting?

711
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:43,110
He's sleeping in there.

712
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,400
Zhu Houyu is such a bad guy.

713
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:48,280
When you were hurt, why didn't you

714
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,550
tell us in the first place?

715
00:42:49,670 --> 00:42:50,920
I was so scared.

716
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,630
If we hadn't asked you,

717
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:54,070
when would you tell us?

718
00:42:57,510 --> 00:42:59,280
Oh, do not tell my parents.

719
00:43:00,030 --> 00:43:01,150
I don't want them to worry.

720
00:43:02,150 --> 00:43:02,990
I know.

721
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:04,710
You don't want them to blame Han Ting.

722
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:09,960
What are you planning

723
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:11,510
about Mr. Han?

724
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:13,920
Will you forgive him?

725
00:43:15,550 --> 00:43:16,550
We're back together.

726
00:43:17,320 --> 00:43:18,320
That's great.

727
00:43:20,150 --> 00:43:21,000
Great.

728
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:22,960
I always think you make a perfect couple.

729
00:43:22,960 --> 00:43:24,070
If you missed each other,

730
00:43:24,070 --> 00:43:25,320
that would be a shame.

731
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:28,630
When you're back together, we'll be relieved.

732
00:43:30,670 --> 00:43:32,070
This is some porridge for you.

733
00:43:32,230 --> 00:43:33,630
We won't disturb him.

734
00:43:33,630 --> 00:43:35,030
Have the porridge before it gets cold.

735
00:43:35,230 --> 00:43:36,110
We will.

736
00:43:36,710 --> 00:43:39,150
Here. A change of clothes for you.

737
00:43:39,280 --> 00:43:40,630
Take good care of Mr. Han.

738
00:43:40,710 --> 00:43:42,070
We'll come and see you tomorrow.

739
00:43:42,110 --> 00:43:42,950
OK.

740
00:43:43,190 --> 00:43:44,710
It's heavy. Can you hold it?

741
00:43:44,710 --> 00:43:45,840
No problem.

742
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:47,480
I just have some scratches.

743
00:43:47,880 --> 00:43:48,760
Be careful.

744
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:49,880
All right. You go back.

745
00:43:50,110 --> 00:43:51,030
You take some good rest.

746
00:43:51,070 --> 00:43:52,510
- I will.
- Rest more.

747
00:44:17,860 --> 00:44:18,700
(Li Li)

748
00:44:19,320 --> 00:44:20,160
Hey, Li Li.

749
00:44:21,110 --> 00:44:22,840
Zhizhou, how's everything in the office?

750
00:44:23,070 --> 00:44:24,440
Everything goes very well.

751
00:44:24,800 --> 00:44:25,840
I've pacified our men.

752
00:44:27,480 --> 00:44:28,320
Glad to hear that.

753
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:30,720
Li Li...

754
00:44:34,070 --> 00:44:34,910
What?

755
00:44:38,710 --> 00:44:39,630
How's Xing?

756
00:44:41,110 --> 00:44:42,230
She has some scratches.

757
00:44:43,110 --> 00:44:44,400
When Xiaomeng and I arrived,

758
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:45,360
Mr. Han was resting.

759
00:44:45,550 --> 00:44:46,550
So, we didn't disturb him.

760
00:44:47,630 --> 00:44:49,630
Glad they're fine. Tomorrow,

761
00:44:50,070 --> 00:44:51,030
shall we go and see them?

762
00:44:51,230 --> 00:44:52,800
OK. See you tomorrow.

763
00:44:53,400 --> 00:44:54,240
See you tomorrow.

764
00:45:22,161 --> 00:45:26,881
♪Once again, you stand opposite me♪

765
00:45:28,981 --> 00:45:33,781
♪Telling the worlds I'm not familiar with♪

766
00:45:35,201 --> 00:45:41,201
♪They seem remote, but get in between us♪

767
00:45:41,991 --> 00:45:46,971
♪We test each other
to see who'll first cross the line♪

768
00:45:49,561 --> 00:45:54,551
♪If I can get closer to you♪

769
00:45:56,291 --> 00:46:01,711
♪Can we have our memories overlapped?♪

770
00:46:02,511 --> 00:46:08,821
♪Time puts walls up to keep my loneliness safe♪

771
00:46:09,491 --> 00:46:16,421
♪Hope understanding will not endanger us♪

772
00:46:18,321 --> 00:46:22,911
♪We each take a side♪

773
00:46:23,351 --> 00:46:29,861
♪The chess board is set,
leaving us with a dilemma♪

774
00:46:30,211 --> 00:46:36,441
♪We always expect each other to relent first♪

775
00:46:36,651 --> 00:46:39,721
♪Before we're relieved♪

776
00:46:39,721 --> 00:46:45,451
♪Pretend love isn't about winning♪

777
00:46:45,721 --> 00:46:50,311
♪We each keep a half♪

778
00:46:50,821 --> 00:46:57,411
♪Completing ourselves before revealing♪

779
00:46:57,641 --> 00:47:00,231
♪Instead of expectations♪

780
00:47:00,231 --> 00:47:07,101
♪We need each other's answer to judge♪

781
00:47:07,101 --> 00:47:12,481
♪When love is a game of exchange♪

782
00:47:13,501 --> 00:47:16,901
♪It is truly terrible♪
